data.description: Cute bungalow in Old Brooklyn. With just a little bit of love or a small job for an investor you could bring this property back to its full potential. There are hardwood floors throughout the living room and 3 bedrooms, an eat-in kitchen and tons of extra storage in the basement. Furnace was replaced in 2018, fenced in yard and newer concrete driveway.  Don’t wait on this one! Selling house as is or 203k or Fannie Home style or any repair type loan. Estimate for home foundation repair in hand.
